title: Hoover WindTunnel T-Series Pet Rewind Going Through Lots Of
description: Hi Luci. We saw your review on our site about your Hoover WindTunnel T-Series Pet Rewind going through a ton of belts and losing suction. We think we know what's wrong, and we put together a quick video to help. Let us know if you need more help! -Amber
